OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first in the south,
OL,6,Fbut sunny spells develop through the
OL,7,Fday. A few spots of drizzle are
OL,8,Fpossible in the south from any thicker
OL,9,Fcloud. Dry in the north with pleasant
OL,10,Fsunny spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPatchy cloud spreads north
OL,13,Ftonight with a few spots of drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces. Fog patches in the south where
OL,15,Fclear spells develop. Chilly in the
OL,16,Fnorth with a rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
