OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FFog patches slow to clear
OL,6,Fin the south. Sunny spells developing
OL,7,Ffor most and feeling warm in the
OL,8,Fsunshine. Clouding over in the far
OL,9,Fnorthwest with outbreaks of rain.
